{"tid":2386812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行路撚】夸父逐日－睇完日出行去睇日落","createTime":"2021-01-29T22:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T10:53:00.000Z","uid":246884,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5540d5489e97fb704b34ef50b276d9d61648e88c","tid":2386812,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T22:32:46.000Z","msg":"話說小弟心血來潮<br />\n想試下跟住個太陽由日出行到日落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vG8ov6C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvG8ov6C.jpg&h=578a7055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線係由大埔行到屯門<br />\n喺大埔海濱公園睇完日出之後<br />\n再行經林村<br />\n最後經元朗入屯門去黃金海岸睇日落<br />\n預計行7個鐘左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNbaa5C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNbaa5C.jpg&h=b176ca99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n計返日照時間有11個鐘<br />\n即係有3到4個鐘飯break同coffee break<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持"},{"pid":"67b1b25c87b3fa081262135abe4ece206476869d","tid":2386812,"uid":258345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T22:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持<br />\n留名睇相"},{"pid":"c0aaa169ea3148891870e68e53803712ff8bf26f","tid":2386812,"uid":202674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T22:35:20.000Z","msg":"勇者"},{"pid":"fe79d7cebe1dc945efd328eb4c1b4987a8c6c36d","tid":2386812,"uid":246884,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T22:39:50.000Z","msg":"06:38 大埔海濱公園<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC1acVV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC1acVV.jpg&h=eb80e6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<